<h1>Projects</h1>

<p>
  Any open source software you create and release to the world is considered a project. This page lists those projects.
</p>

<p>
  On an ongoing basis, the economic activity generated by OSC citizens is attributed to your open source projects. At the moment, <strong><%= number_with_delimiter @hashes_count_sum %></strong> hashes have (so far) been attributed to your projects - earning you money.
</p>

<h2>
  Projects list
</h2>

<dl>
  <% @projects.each do |project| %>
    <dt>
      <%= link_to project.url, project_path(url: project.url), target: '_blank' %>
      <dd>
        <%= number_with_delimiter project.hashes_count %> hashes and <%= number_with_delimiter project.stars_count %> stars.
        <%= link_to '🐦', tweet_url(project.url) %>
        <br/>
      </dd>
    </dt>
  <% end %>
</dl>
